data.description: Welcome to 224 20th Ave S, where modern comfort meets timeless '70s charm! This well maintained 4-level home offers a spacious layout designed to accommodate the whole family. You'll find all 3 bedrooms conveniently located on one level, with a large primary bathroom upstairs. The kitchen opens into a bright dining space, with breakfast bar for two. A sliding glass door off the dining area not only grants access to the deck and backyard but also supplies the interior loads of natural light. In the lower level, where you'll discover a versatile den, a sleek wet bar, and a recreational space that's perfect for a variety of activities. The home retains many charming original '70s design elements, including distinctive ceiling beams, cedar shakes, and a round wet bar, adding character and uniqueness to the space. Situated just steps away from Jefferson Park, this location offers easy access to public transportation, shopping and schools.
